defaultSRDP grants are set up to benefit large landowners and are extremely difficult for community groups to access. They do not recognise the need or pathway to accommodate them.
default&#xa0;
defaultAny public subsidy should bring with it some public ownership. The poor are being fleeced to subsidise the rich in many cases.
